text: The pilot programme is coming to an end today so I would like to thank you for your enthusiasm throughout our mentoring session, I can happily say that you have taught me a lot about myself and given me confidence to go on and do this more in the future. Good luck with your studies and careers, I have no doubt you will go on to do amazing things. If you would like to keep in contact you can find me on LinkedIn, my full name is Graham Phelan :blush: good luck!

Thank you so much! Honestly and truly, I have realised that this is really the career that I want to go into and I can go in with confidence knowing I have more knowledge than before. I was a little hesitant before having unanswered questions but you have answered them all and beyond. Thank you, thank you, thank you!!
